snippet.title: THE VTUBER SUMMIT - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
It's you vs 100 VTubers on a journey to make your dream come true, in this RPG fangame, featuring a miscellany of various VTubers and creators - releasing for PC and MacOS on August 2023! Are you ready?

If you can't wait, sign up for the closed beta below! 
https://vtubersummit.com/cbt/
Applications are open until February 10.

Follow updates for the game on Twitter:
https://twitter.com/thevtubersummit


==== Credits ====
Key Art: NeonLab
Animation: @JusagiChan 
Trailer Music: @JoelArmishawComposer 

#VTuber
#ENVtuber
